.TH Declare-BashScript 1 "October 2025" "docker-homebridge" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
Declare-BashScript \- Bash script argument and option parsing helper
.SH SYNOPSIS
source Declare-BashScript <script_path> <long-options> <short-options>
.SH DESCRIPTION
Provides argument parsing, usage, error, note, and success functions for bash scripts. Intended to be sourced at the top of other scripts.
.SH USAGE
source Declare-BashScript $0 "help,verbose,path:," "hvp" "$@"
.SH OPTIONS
Options are passed via <long-options> and <short-options> arguments.
